Package be.stevenroose.javastar

Interface Summary
Cost<MyCost> This class is used to represent costs and heuristic values.
Node Node classes should extend this abstract class.
 

Class Summary
AstarCalculator<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>> The actual A star calculation happens within this class.
AstarHelper<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>> This class is where most calculations are performed.
AstarResult<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>> This class represents the result of an A star calculation.
PathNode<N extends Node,C extends Cost<C>> This class represents nodes in the graph while the algorithm is expanding it.
 

Enum Summary
AstarResult.ResultType All the possible types a result can have.
 

Exception Summary
AstarHelper.NodesNotAdjacentException The exception exists because certain methods used in this class only accept nodes that are adjacent to each other.
